

This project is used to show sample code to use the GateIn/eXo Organization Service.

The current version contains a simple Java class and REST service to create user and add user to a group.

Once you have build and deploy the Jar to your library folder you can test it using the following URLs:

To create a user :

    [server]/rest/extensions/users/add?userName=[user]&email=[email]&firstName=[first]&lastName=[last]&password=[password]

To Add a user to a group

    [server]/rest/extensions/users/addMembership?userName=[user]&groupName=[partners]&membershipType=[member]

To come:

    Mapp all methods of the different handlers to manage the different administration operation using rest


